msgctxt "760_Saejima"
msgid "(So, what should I talk about?)"
msgstr "(Bueno, ¿qué podría decir?)."

msgctxt "808_Sugiyama"
msgid "...This conversation's got me fired up! I'm going to work harder so that I can be like you, Saejima-san!"
msgstr "...This conversation's got me fired up! I'm going to work harder so that I can be like you, Saejima-san!"

msgctxt "820_Saejima"
msgid "(Looks like he's motivated now.)"
msgstr "(Parece que ahora está motivado.)"

msgctxt "868_Sugiyama"
msgid "I see. Thank you for the information. The lesson is that I have to use my head if I want to be a better fighter. Got it."
msgstr "I see. Thank you for the information. The lesson is that I have to use my head if I want to be a better fighter. Got it."

msgctxt "880_Saejima"
msgid "(He looks a little more motivated.)"
msgstr "(He looks a little more motivated.)"

msgctxt "928_Sugiyama"
msgid "Hahaha! That's hilarious! But..."
msgstr "Hahaha! That's hilarious! But..."

msgctxt "940_Sugiyama"
msgid "Should I be laughing now? I'm sure other people are still at their dojos, training... And I'm here drinking and laughing..."
msgstr "Should I be laughing now? I'm sure other people are still at their dojos, training... And I'm here drinking and laughing..."

msgctxt "952_Saejima"
msgid "(I shoulda talked about somethin' else...)"
msgstr "(I shoulda talked about somethin' else...)"

msgctxt "964_Saejima"
msgid "(So, what should I talk about?)"
msgstr "(Bueno, ¿qué podría decir?)."

msgctxt "1012_Sugiyama"
msgid "You're amazing, Saejima-san! But compared to you, I'm nothing..."
msgstr "You're amazing, Saejima-san! But compared to you, I'm nothing..."

msgctxt "1024_Saejima"
msgid "(Looks like he's depressed now...)"
msgstr "(Looks like he's depressed now...)"

msgctxt "1072_Sugiyama"
msgid "That kind of thing happens to you, too? I feel like I know you a little better now. Heheh."
msgstr "That kind of thing happens to you, too? I feel like I know you a little better now. Heheh."

msgctxt "1084_Saejima"
msgid "(Our relationship's grown stronger...)"
msgstr "(Our relationship's grown stronger...)"

msgctxt "1132_Sugiyama"
msgid "I see. So that's what made you a strong fighter. That's interesting."
msgstr "I see. So that's what made you a strong fighter. That's interesting."

msgctxt "1144_Saejima"
msgid "(Guess that went okay.)"
msgstr "(Supongo que salió bien)."

msgctxt "1156_Saejima"
msgid "(So, what should I talk about?)"
msgstr "(Bueno, ¿qué podría decir?)."

msgctxt "1204_Sugiyama"
msgid "Wow, you're really knowledgeable. I wish I was so well informed."
msgstr "Wow, you're really knowledgeable. I wish I was so well informed."

msgctxt "1216_Saejima"
msgid "(Guess that went okay.)"
msgstr "(Supongo que salió bien)."

msgctxt "1264_Sugiyama"
msgid "I don't know too much about math... Sorry."
msgstr "I don't know too much about math... Sorry."

msgctxt "1276_Saejima"
msgid "(Guess he ain't a big fan o' the topic.)"
msgstr "(No creo que le agrade mucho el tema)."

msgctxt "1324_Sugiyama"
msgid "You really know about everything, Saejima-san! I'm really interested in hearing more!"
msgstr "You really know about everything, Saejima-san! I'm really interested in hearing more!"

msgctxt "1336_Saejima"
msgid "(Looks like he opened up a bit. Perfect.)"
msgstr "(Parece que ya se soltó más. Perfecto)."

msgctxt "1348_Saejima"
msgid "(So, what should I talk about?)"
msgstr "(Bueno, ¿qué podría decir?)."

msgctxt "1396_Sugiyama"
msgid "I see. That may just work! If I do it right, I wonder if I can even get Mayako-chan to like me..."
msgstr "I see. That may just work! If I do it right, I wonder if I can even get Mayako-chan to like me..."

msgctxt "1408_Saejima"
msgid "(Guess that went okay.)"
msgstr "(Supongo que salió bien)."

msgctxt "1456_Sugiyama"
msgid "You're totally right, Saejima-san! Men are meant to love a single woman for all eternity!"
msgstr "You're totally right, Saejima-san! Men are meant to love a single woman for all eternity!"

msgctxt "1468_Saejima"
msgid "(Looks like he opened up a bit. Perfect.)"
msgstr "(Parece que ya se soltó más. Perfecto)."

msgctxt "1516_Sugiyama"
msgid "But Mayako-chan is the only one in my life! I would never cheat on her! That's just impure!"
msgstr "But Mayako-chan is the only one in my life! I would never cheat on her! That's just impure!"

msgctxt "1528_Saejima"
msgid "(Guess he ain't a big fan o' the topic.)"
msgstr "(No creo que le agrade mucho el tema)."

msgctxt "1540_Saejima"
msgid "(So, what should I talk about?)"
msgstr "(Bueno, ¿qué podría decir?)."

msgctxt "1588_Sugiyama"
msgid "It's best to dream big, right? I'll always make sure to aim big and work hard!"
msgstr "It's best to dream big, right? I'll always make sure to aim big and work hard!"

msgctxt "1600_Saejima"
msgid "(Looks like he opened up a bit. Perfect.)"
msgstr "(Parece que ya se soltó más. Perfecto)."

msgctxt "1648_Sugiyama"
msgid "I see. I shouldn't just dream about my future. I should make an actual life plan... Hm... That sounds pretty difficult."
msgstr "I see. I shouldn't just dream about my future. I should make an actual life plan... Hm... That sounds pretty difficult."

msgctxt "1660_Saejima"
msgid "(Guess that went okay.)"
msgstr "(Supongo que salió bien)."

msgctxt "1708_Sugiyama"
msgid " That sounds like a lot of fun, but... I don't think that's going to work forever. I think I should live maturely and have goals."
msgstr " That sounds like a lot of fun, but... I don't think that's going to work forever. I think I should live maturely and have goals."

msgctxt "1720_Saejima"
msgid "(Guess he ain't a big fan o' the topic.)"
msgstr "(No creo que le agrade mucho el tema)."

msgctxt "1732_Saejima"
msgid "(So, what should I talk about?)"
msgstr "(Bueno, ¿qué podría decir?)."

msgctxt "1780_Sugiyama"
msgid "You're really knowledgeable. I should take better care of my appearance, too."
msgstr "You're really knowledgeable. I should take better care of my appearance, too."

msgctxt "1792_Saejima"
msgid "(Looks like he opened up a bit. Perfect.)"
msgstr "(Parece que ya se soltó más. Perfecto)."

msgctxt "1840_Sugiyama"
msgid "I'm not sure I want to talk about that. I'm kind of broke, so..."
msgstr "I'm not sure I want to talk about that. I'm kind of broke, so..."

msgctxt "1852_Saejima"
msgid "(Guess he ain't a big fan o' the topic.)"
msgstr "(No creo que le agrade mucho el tema)."

msgctxt "1900_Sugiyama"
msgid "Drinking really is fun. But a lot of times I'm hung over the next day and feel down. Heheh..."
msgstr "Drinking really is fun. But a lot of times I'm hung over the next day and feel down. Heheh..."

msgctxt "1912_Saejima"
msgid "(Guess that went okay.)"
msgstr "(Supongo que salió bien)."

msgctxt "1948_Saejima"
msgid "By the way, you got a hobby or somethin'?"
msgstr "By the way, you got a hobby or somethin'?"

msgctxt "1960_Sugiyama"
msgid "A hobby? Hm... If I had to choose, I would say listening to music."
msgstr "A hobby? Hm... If I had to choose, I would say listening to music."

msgctxt "1972_Saejima"
msgid "That ain't a bad hobby. So what kind o' music ya listen to?"
msgstr "That ain't a bad hobby. So what kind o' music ya listen to?"

msgctxt "1984_Sugiyama"
msgid "Lots of things, really. But I guess I'm really into techno."
msgstr "Lots of things, really. But I guess I'm really into techno."

msgctxt "1996_Saejima"
msgid "Techno...? What's that?"
msgstr "Techno...? What's that?"

msgctxt "2008_Sugiyama"
msgid "Huh? Saejima-san, you mean to say that you don't know about techno!?"
msgstr "Huh? Saejima-san, you mean to say that you don't know about techno!?"

msgctxt "2020_Saejima"
msgid "Hmph... 'Course I know."
msgstr "Hmph... 'Course I know."

msgctxt "2032_Sugiyama"
msgid "Really!? That's a surprise!"
msgstr "Really!? That's a surprise!"

msgctxt "2044_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah, techno, right? Just ain't heard that word in a long time. An old buddy o' mine used to do the jitterbug."
msgstr "Yeah, techno, right? Just ain't heard that word in a long time. An old buddy o' mine used to do the jitterbug."

msgctxt "2056_Sugiyama"
msgid "The jitterbug...?"
msgstr "The jitterbug...?"

msgctxt "2068_Saejima"
msgid "That's right. Jitterbug's the dance, ain't it? The techno jitterbug. Everybody knows that."
msgstr "That's right. Jitterbug's the dance, ain't it? The techno jitterbug. Everybody knows that."

msgctxt "2080_Sugiyama"
msgid "Oh... Right..."
msgstr "Oh... Right..."

msgctxt "2092_Saejima"
msgid "If ya like techno, then maybe you should try learnin' the jitterbug, too. Whaddya think? If ya need help, I guess I could..."
msgstr "If ya like techno, then maybe you should try learnin' the jitterbug, too. Whaddya think? If ya need help, I guess I could..."

msgctxt "2104_Sugiyama"
msgid "No thanks! I won't be needing any help! Thanks for the offer though!"
msgstr "No thanks! I won't be needing any help! Thanks for the offer though!"

msgctxt "2116_Saejima"
msgid "(Hmph. What's his problem?)"
msgstr "(Hmph. What's his problem?)"

msgctxt "2128_Saejima"
msgid "Hmph... 'Course I know. Techno... Short for technology..."
msgstr "Hmph... 'Course I know. Techno... Short for technology..."

msgctxt "2140_Sugiyama"
msgid "Um... Saejima-san... If you don't know what it is, you should just say so."
msgstr "Um... Saejima-san... If you don't know what it is, you should just say so."

msgctxt "2152_Saejima"
msgid "Right..."
msgstr "Cierto..."

msgctxt "2164_Saejima"
msgid "(Did he lose trust in me...?)"
msgstr "(Did he lose trust in me...?)"

msgctxt "2176_Saejima"
msgid "Techno...? Never heard of it. But I used to listen to traditional Japanese ballads n' folk."
msgstr "Techno...? Never heard of it. But I used to listen to traditional Japanese ballads n' folk."

msgctxt "2188_Sugiyama"
msgid "You know, I had that impression about you."
msgstr "You know, I had that impression about you."

msgctxt "2200_Saejima"
msgid "Singers of Japanese ballads n' folk have real soul. Just listenin' to 'em gets me motivated. Y'know, you should try listenin' yourself."
msgstr "Singers of Japanese ballads n' folk have real soul. Just listenin' to 'em gets me motivated. Y'know, you should try listenin' yourself."

msgctxt "2212_Sugiyama"
msgid "Maybe I will. Hearing you talk about it makes me want to listen to it! I think I'll try listening to some traditional Japanese ballads before practice!"
msgstr "Maybe I will. Hearing you talk about it makes me want to listen to it! I think I'll try listening to some traditional Japanese ballads before practice!"

msgctxt "2224_Saejima"
msgid "(Looks like he's motivated now.)"
msgstr "(Parece que ahora está motivado.)"

msgctxt "2236_Sugiyama"
msgid "Do you remember how I told you that I'd ask Mayako-chan out if I won in a tournament?"
msgstr "Do you remember how I told you that I'd ask Mayako-chan out if I won in a tournament?"

msgctxt "2248_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah. I remember."
msgstr "Sí, lo recuerdo."

msgctxt "2260_Sugiyama"
msgid "Well, if I actually do win and I have to ask her out, what do you think I should say?"
msgstr "Well, if I actually do win and I have to ask her out, what do you think I should say?"

msgctxt "2272_Saejima"
msgid "That ain't my problem..."
msgstr "Ese no es mi problema..."

msgctxt "2284_Sugiyama"
msgid "But... I've never asked someone out before."
msgstr "But... I've never asked someone out before."

msgctxt "2296_Sugiyama"
msgid "You're pretty much the only person that I have to ask about things like this. Please, Saejima-san! Just give me some idea!"
msgstr "You're pretty much the only person that I have to ask about things like this. Please, Saejima-san! Just give me some idea!"

msgctxt "2308_Saejima"
msgid "Hmph... Fine. So ya wanna know how to ask her out? All ya gotta say is..."
msgstr "Hmph... Fine. So ya wanna know how to ask her out? All ya gotta say is..."

msgctxt "2320_Saejima"
msgid "It's best to be straightforward. Just say, \"I love you!\""
msgstr "It's best to be straightforward. Just say, \"I love you!\""

msgctxt "2332_Sugiyama"
msgid "Yeah, that's it! It's best to say it in a manly and straightforward way!"
msgstr "Yeah, that's it! It's best to say it in a manly and straightforward way!"

msgctxt "2344_Sugiyama"
msgid "I love love love love love love love love love love love love love love love love love love looooooooooove you!"
msgstr "I love love love love love love love love love love love love love love love love love love looooooooooove you!"

msgctxt "2356_Sugiyama"
msgid "Like that!? Boy, it really does feel good when you say it so directly like that!"
msgstr "Like that!? Boy, it really does feel good when you say it so directly like that!"

msgctxt "2368_Saejima"
msgid "(Ain't exactly what I meant, but... Oh, well.)"
msgstr "(Ain't exactly what I meant, but... Oh, well.)"

msgctxt "2380_Saejima"
msgid "Say, \"Make me breakfast every mornin', woman!\" Men have been usin' that line for generations. I'm sure it'll still work today."
msgstr "Say, \"Make me breakfast every mornin', woman!\" Men have been usin' that line for generations. I'm sure it'll still work today."

msgctxt "2392_Sugiyama"
msgid "Oh! That's a pretty good line! I love eating breakfast, too. Thanks, Saejima-san!"
msgstr "Oh! That's a pretty good line! I love eating breakfast, too. Thanks, Saejima-san!"

msgctxt "2404_Saejima"
msgid "It ain't supposed to be 'bout whether ya like breakfast or not..."
msgstr "It ain't supposed to be 'bout whether ya like breakfast or not..."

msgctxt "2416_Sugiyama"
msgid "I'm sure that Mayako-chan can make a delicious breakfast... Mmmm... Breakfast with Mayako-chan... Mmm..."
msgstr "I'm sure that Mayako-chan can make a delicious breakfast... Mmmm... Breakfast with Mayako-chan... Mmm..."

msgctxt "2428_Saejima"
msgid "Umm... Hideo...?"
msgstr "Umm... ¿Hideo...?"

msgctxt "2440_Sugiyama"
msgid "I feel totally pumped now! Mayako-chan's breakfasts are for me only! Haha! I am definitely going to win the tournament and have me that breakfast!"
msgstr "I feel totally pumped now! Mayako-chan's breakfasts are for me only! Haha! I am definitely going to win the tournament and have me that breakfast!"

msgctxt "2452_Saejima"
msgid "(Ain't exactly what I meant, but at least he seems motivated...)"
msgstr "(Ain't exactly what I meant, but at least he seems motivated...)"

msgctxt "2464_Saejima"
msgid "How 'bout, \"May I ask for your daughter's hand in marriage!?\" Heheh."
msgstr "How 'bout, \"May I ask for your daughter's hand in marriage!?\" Heheh."

msgctxt "2476_Sugiyama"
msgid "Saejima-san... I'm asking you for real. This isn't some lame joke."
msgstr "Saejima-san... I'm asking you for real. This isn't some lame joke."

msgctxt "2488_Sugiyama"
msgid "It's not a question for Mayako-chan's father. Will you take me seriously for a minute? I thought you understood. Just... never mind."
msgstr "It's not a question for Mayako-chan's father. Will you take me seriously for a minute? I thought you understood. Just... never mind."

msgctxt "2500_Saejima"
msgid "(Guess he can't take a joke...)"
msgstr "(Guess he can't take a joke...)"

msgctxt "2512_Sugiyama"
msgid "Once I get a girlfriend, I have to take her out on dates, right?"
msgstr "Once I get a girlfriend, I have to take her out on dates, right?"

msgctxt "2524_Saejima"
msgid "Guess so."
msgstr "Supongo."

msgctxt "2536_Sugiyama"
msgid "If Mayako-chan becomes my girlfriend, where do you think I should take her on a date?"
msgstr "If Mayako-chan becomes my girlfriend, where do you think I should take her on a date?"

msgctxt "2548_Saejima"
msgid "A movie theater is the safest bet."
msgstr "A movie theater is the safest bet."

msgctxt "2560_Sugiyama"
msgid "I see. The classic dinner and a movie."
msgstr "Ya veo. La clásica de comida y una película."

msgctxt "2572_Saejima"
msgid "That's right. You'll just be watchin' a movie, so you got nothin' else to worry about. It's the easiest way to date."
msgstr "That's right. You'll just be watchin' a movie, so you got nothin' else to worry about. It's the easiest way to date."

msgctxt "2584_Sugiyama"
msgid "Hm, that's a pretty sad reason, but at least we'd be able to stay within the city. Thanks for the info."
msgstr "Hm, that's a pretty sad reason, but at least we'd be able to stay within the city. Thanks for the info."

msgctxt "2596_Saejima"
msgid "(Hm... Guess that went okay.)"
msgstr "(Hm... Guess that went okay.)"

msgctxt "2608_Saejima"
msgid "How 'bout hiking? Hiking in the mountains sounds fun, don't it?"
msgstr "How 'bout hiking? Hiking in the mountains sounds fun, don't it?"

msgctxt "2620_Sugiyama"
msgid "Hiking...? I don't think that's the best idea. I don't want to wear myself out."
msgstr "Hiking...? I don't think that's the best idea. I don't want to wear myself out."

msgctxt "2632_Saejima"
msgid "That's the point. It's a good chance to show her how strong ya are and how hard you've worked to get so strong. Get it?"
msgstr "That's the point. It's a good chance to show her how strong ya are and how hard you've worked to get so strong. Get it?"

msgctxt "2644_Sugiyama"
msgid "Ohhh! I see! She's sure to fall for me after watching how strong I am pushing up that mountain!"
msgstr "Ohhh! I see! She's sure to fall for me after watching how strong I am pushing up that mountain!"

msgctxt "2656_Sugiyama"
msgid "Wow, what a great idea, Saejima-san! I'd better go and train more for our hiking trip! This is going to be great!"
msgstr "Wow, what a great idea, Saejima-san! I'd better go and train more for our hiking trip! This is going to be great!"

msgctxt "2668_Saejima"
msgid "(Looks like he's motivated now. Guess I can give some pretty good advice.)"
msgstr "(Looks like he's motivated now. Guess I can give some pretty good advice.)"

msgctxt "2680_Saejima"
msgid "Discos are popular. No question about it. Disco fever till mornin'. Sound good, right?"
msgstr "Discos are popular. No question about it. Disco fever till mornin'. Sound good, right?"

msgctxt "2692_Sugiyama"
msgid "Disco...!? Ohhh, you're talking about clubs!"
msgstr "Disco...!? Ohhh, you're talking about clubs!"

msgctxt "2704_Sugiyama"
msgid "Yeah, that may actually be a good idea. Mayako-chan does like music."
msgstr "Yeah, that may actually be a good idea. Mayako-chan does like music."

msgctxt "2716_Saejima"
msgid "Club...? What's that? A disco's a place where ya go to dance. Didn't ya know that?"
msgstr "Club...? What's that? A disco's a place where ya go to dance. Didn't ya know that?"

msgctxt "2728_Sugiyama"
msgid "Hmmm, I don't even know where to begin explaining. Never mind. I got it... Thank you for the advice... I guess..."
msgstr "Hmmm, I don't even know where to begin explaining. Never mind. I got it... Thank you for the advice... I guess..."

msgctxt "2740_Saejima"
msgid "(Hmm... Our conversation ain't clickin'.)"
msgstr "(Hmm... Our conversation ain't clickin'.)"

msgctxt "2752_Sugiyama"
msgid "Hmmm... Hmmm..."
msgstr "Hmmm... Hmmm..."

msgctxt "2764_Saejima"
msgid "You're still tryin' to decide what to order?"
msgstr "You're still tryin' to decide what to order?"

msgctxt "2776_Sugiyama"
msgid "Yeah. I'm a really indecisive person. I even have trouble ordering food..."
msgstr "Yeah. I'm a really indecisive person. I even have trouble ordering food..."

msgctxt "2788_Sugiyama"
msgid "Tea or beer? I just can't decide... I guess I'll go with beer. But maybe I shouldn't drink today... Hmm..."
msgstr "Tea or beer? I just can't decide... I guess I'll go with beer. But maybe I shouldn't drink today... Hmm..."

msgctxt "2800_Saejima"
msgid "Be a man. Make up yer mind already."
msgstr "Be a man. Make up yer mind already."

msgctxt "2812_Sugiyama"
msgid "But..."
msgstr "Pero..."

msgctxt "2824_Saejima"
msgid "Makin' split-second decisions is vital, even when fightin'. You should make it a habit to decide on things quickly."
msgstr "Makin' split-second decisions is vital, even when fightin'. You should make it a habit to decide on things quickly."

msgctxt "2836_Sugiyama"
msgid "Good point! So you're saying my daily habits affect my fighting skills, too! That's some deep logic! You really are something, Saejima-san!"
msgstr "Good point! So you're saying my daily habits affect my fighting skills, too! That's some deep logic! You really are something, Saejima-san!"

msgctxt "2848_Saejima"
msgid "(Heheh. Looks like he's pretty motivated now. Guess I can give some good advice sometimes.)"
msgstr "(Heheh. Looks like he's pretty motivated now. Guess I can give some good advice sometimes.)"

msgctxt "2860_Saejima"
msgid "No rush. Just take yer time. Everybody should work at their own pace."
msgstr "No rush. Just take yer time. Everybody should work at their own pace."

msgctxt "2872_Sugiyama"
msgid "Thanks, Saejima-san... Then I guess I'll just take my time deciding..."
msgstr "Thanks, Saejima-san... Then I guess I'll just take my time deciding..."

msgctxt "2884_Sugiyama"
msgid "Okay. Let's see..."
msgstr "Okay. Let's see..."

msgctxt "2896_Sugiyama"
msgid "Maybe some Fried Gyoza would be good..."
msgstr "Maybe some Fried Gyoza would be good..."

msgctxt "2908_Sugiyama"
msgid "No... But I just had some the other day, so..."
msgstr "No... But I just had some the other day, so..."

msgctxt "2920_Sugiyama"
msgid "Hmmm..."
msgstr "Mmmm..."

msgctxt "2932_Saejima"
msgid "Made up yer mind yet?"
msgstr "Made up yer mind yet?"

msgctxt "2944_Sugiyama"
msgid "Don't rush me! Ugh, I just can't decide! Life really is like a long chain of decisions that you have to make. It's not easy!"
msgstr "¡No me apures! ¡No me puedo decidir! La vida es realmente como una larga cadena de decisiones que hay que elegir. ¡No es fácil!"

msgctxt "2956_Saejima"
msgid "(Hurry up n' decide already...)"
msgstr "(Es el momento, decídete...)"

msgctxt "2968_Saejima"
msgid "Enough! Gimme the damn menu! Organic Soybean Yose Dofu! Done! No more dither datherin'!"
msgstr "Enough! Gimme the damn menu! Organic Soybean Yose Dofu! Done! No more dither datherin'!"

msgctxt "2980_Sugiyama"
msgid "But, but! Why do you have to be so mean? I was just about to say that I wanted the Fried Gyoza..."
msgstr "But, but! Why do you have to be so mean? I was just about to say that I wanted the Fried Gyoza..."

msgctxt "2992_Saejima"
msgid "(Was I a bit too harsh...?)"
msgstr "(Was I a bit too harsh...?)"

msgctxt "3016_Sugiyama"
msgid "Aaah... A nice cold beer is the best! Especially after a hard day of training."
msgstr "Aaah... A nice cold beer is the best! Especially after a hard day of training."

msgctxt "3028_Saejima"
msgid "Got that right. So tell me, why'd you decide to start fightin'?"
msgstr "Got that right. So tell me, why'd you decide to start fightin'?"

msgctxt "3040_Sugiyama"
msgid "The reason I started? Well, it's not a very noble reason, but..."
msgstr "The reason I started? Well, it's not a very noble reason, but..."

msgctxt "3052_Saejima"
msgid "Just tell me already."
msgstr "Just tell me already."

msgctxt "3064_Sugiyama"
msgid "I did it to get a girl that I like to notice me."
msgstr "I did it to get a girl that I like to notice me."

msgctxt "3076_Saejima"
msgid "Whaddya talkin' about?"
msgstr "Whaddya talkin' about?"

msgctxt "3088_Sugiyama"
msgid "There's this girl named Mayako-chan that I've had a crush on for a while. She's really cute and sweet..."
msgstr "There's this girl named Mayako-chan that I've had a crush on for a while. She's really cute and sweet..."

msgctxt "3100_Sugiyama"
msgid "If possible, I'd like to make her my girlfriend. But I'm not very special and I lack confidence. She's sure to say no even if I could ask her."
msgstr "If possible, I'd like to make her my girlfriend. But I'm not very special and I lack confidence. She's sure to say no even if I could ask her."

msgctxt "3112_Saejima"
msgid "Huh. So ya wanted to get stronger and gain confidence in yerself."
msgstr "Huh. So ya wanted to get stronger and gain confidence in yerself."

msgctxt "3124_Sugiyama"
msgid "Exactly. I want to become a man that's worthy to be by her side. I started fighting to gain the confidence to ask her out."
msgstr "Exactly. I want to become a man that's worthy to be by her side. I started fighting to gain the confidence to ask her out."

msgctxt "3136_Sugiyama"
msgid "It's an impure reason, right?"
msgstr "It's an impure reason, right?"

msgctxt "3148_Saejima"
msgid "No. The reason you started ain't important. It's what you do afterwards that counts."
msgstr "No. The reason you started ain't important. It's what you do afterwards that counts."

msgctxt "3160_Saejima"
msgid "Follow through on what ya decide. That's what men do. If you really like that girl, give it everythin' ya got. Show her what you can do."
msgstr "Follow through on what ya decide. That's what men do. If you really like that girl, give it everythin' ya got. Show her what you can do."

msgctxt "3172_Sugiyama"
msgid "Saejima-san... Thank you. I'll train hard so that I can be proud of who I am!"
msgstr "Saejima-san... Thank you. I'll train hard so that I can be proud of who I am!"

msgctxt "3184_Saejima"
msgid "(Looks like he's pretty motivated now. Guess I can give some good advice sometimes.)"
msgstr "(Looks like he's pretty motivated now. Guess I can give some good advice sometimes.)"

msgctxt "3196_Saejima"
msgid "No, it ain't impure. It's actually a real good reason."
msgstr "No, it ain't impure. It's actually a real good reason."

msgctxt "3208_Saejima"
msgid "Becomin' a better person to achieve a goal is a respectable attitude. Even if it's for a girl."
msgstr "Becomin' a better person to achieve a goal is a respectable attitude. Even if it's for a girl."

msgctxt "3220_Sugiyama"
msgid "Saejima-san... Thank you. I actually felt really guilty about that for the longest time. I feel better now, though."
msgstr "Saejima-san... Thank you. I actually felt really guilty about that for the longest time. I feel better now, though."

msgctxt "3232_Saejima"
msgid "(Well, looks like he's a bit more motivated.)"
msgstr "(Well, looks like he's a bit more motivated.)"

msgctxt "3244_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah, that ain't a good enough reason. You'll never grow stronger if you're trainin' for such a lame goal."
msgstr "Yeah, that ain't a good enough reason. You'll never grow stronger if you're trainin' for such a lame goal."

msgctxt "3256_Saejima"
msgid "Plus, it's pathetic that you ain't got the guts to ask the girl out. If you like her, just tell her how ya feel. It ain't rocket science."
msgstr "Plus, it's pathetic that you ain't got the guts to ask the girl out. If you like her, just tell her how ya feel. It ain't rocket science."

msgctxt "3268_Sugiyama"
msgid "I know, but... Never mind... Just forget that I brought it up..."
msgstr "I know, but... Never mind... Just forget that I brought it up..."

